  "page": "Regis Groves",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Groves\" title=\"House Groves\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Regis Groves</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/50px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/75px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/100px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Groves\" title=\"House Groves\">House Groves</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/132_AC\" title=\"132 AC\">132&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Regis Groves</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Groves\" title=\"House Groves\">House Groves</a>. He became a <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Regis_Groves&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser Regis supported the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a> appointed him and four other blacks to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/131_AC\" title=\"131 AC\">131&#160;AC</a> after the civil war ended.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> had fallen under the sway of an alleged \"witch queen\", <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a>, after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_Above_the_Gods_Eye\" title=\"Battle Above the Gods Eye\">Battle Above the Gods Eye</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>. Since <a href=\"/index.php/Broken_men\" title=\"Broken men\">broken men</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaws\" title=\"Outlaws\">outlaws</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Robber_knight\" title=\"Robber knight\">robber knights</a> preyed upon the countryside, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tyland_Lannister\" title=\"Tyland Lannister\">Tyland Lannister</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, tasked Regis with reclaiming Harrenhal in <a href=\"/index.php/132_AC\" title=\"132 AC\">132&#160;AC</a>. Regis marched with half a hundred men to <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Darry\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Castle Darry\">Castle Darry</a>, where he was joined by a like number under Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Darry\" title=\"Damon Darry\">Damon Darry</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When the king's men arrived at Harrenhal they found the gates barred and six hundred people within, a third of them warriors. Alys claimed to be the widow of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a>, who had died during the Dance, and that <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers%27s_son\" title=\"Alys Rivers&#39;s son\">the young boy</a> with her was her trueborn son by Aemond. Alys commanded Regis to kneel to her son and swear his sword to the rightful king, but Regis laughed at her and refused to do so. Some say the sorceress raised a hand and caused Regis's skull to burst, while others state Regis was killed by a crossbow bolt through his eye. The <a href=\"/index.php/Fool\" title=\"Fool\">fool</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Mushroom\" title=\"Mushroom\">Mushroom</a>, who was not present, claims it was a lead ball from a sling. Alys's riders charged out through Harrenhal's gates and defeated the king's men in a bloody rout, with Damon leading the survivors back to Darry.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Regis's death disturbed Tyland, and <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">Aegon's regents</a> agreed that a larger army should be gathered to reclaim Harrenhal.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Regis_Groves&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I do not kneel to <a href=\"/index.php/Bastards\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastards\">bastards</a>, much less <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers%27s_son\" title=\"Alys Rivers&#39;s son\">the baseborn whelp</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">a kinslayer</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Wet_nurse\" title=\"Wet nurse\">a milk cow</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Regis to <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Regis_Groves&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Hooded Hand.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\