=\"/index.php/Raynard_Ruskyn\" title=\"Raynard Ruskyn\">Raynard Ruskyn</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Members</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>Ser <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Regis Groves</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Amaury_Peake\" title=\"Amaury Peake\">Amaury Peake</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Mervyn_Flowers\" title=\"Mervyn Flowers\">Mervyn Flowers</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmund_Warrick\" title=\"Edmund Warrick\">Edmund Warrick</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Dennis_Whitfield\" title=\"Dennis Whitfield\">Dennis Whitfield</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Agramore_Cobb\" title=\"Agramore Cobb\">Agramore Cobb</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Staunton\" title=\"Joffrey Staunton\">Joffrey Staunton</a></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_II)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Viserys II)\">Aemon Targaryen</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robin_Massey\" title=\"Robin Massey\">Robin Massey</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Darklyn\" title=\"Robert Darklyn\">Robert Darklyn</a> were named respectively as member and Lord Commander of the Kingsguard by Aegon III,<br />but the appointment was later set aside by <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Lord Regent</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Unwin_Peake\" title=\"Unwin Peake\">Unwin Peake</a>.\n</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403130651\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 